                <div class="alert alert-info col-12 col-lg-10 rounded-8 shadow-sm" role="alert">
                    <b>Note</b><br>
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            Card-not-present (CNP) is a card payment transaction where the cardholder is not physically
                            present at the merchant when payment is made.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            CNP transaction includes:
                            <ol style="list-style-type: lower-roman;">
                                <li>Non-secured online transaction</li>
                                <li>Mail Order Telephone Order</li>
                                <li>
                                    Recurring / Auto Debit transaction (i.e. telephone bill / utilities bill / insurance
                                    premiums etc)
                                </li>
                            </ol>
                        </li>
                        <li>Overseas transaction is a transaction performed outside of Malaysia.</li>
                        <li>
                            Overseas transaction includes:
                            <ol style="list-style-type: lower-roman;">
                                <li>Cash withdrawal at overseas ATM</li>
                                <li>Overseas point-of-sale purchase ("POS")</li>
                            </ol>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Opting-in a card incorporates both CNP and overseas transaction. Failing to opt-in your Card
                            for overseas transaction will not permit any transactions abroad.
                        </li>
                        <li>This function allows you to change your current opt status</li>
                        <li>To change the opt out or in status, click on the new opt status</li>
                        <li>
                            Please call the Self Service Terminal Call Centre at +603-2179 5000 if you require further
                            information.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
